        {
          "id": 3,
          "background": "/images/school2.jpg",
          "narrations": [
            {
              "name": "intro",
              "text": ["At school, your teacher tells you to redo one of your assignments by tomorrow. The feedback causes you significant stress along with your other responsibilities. You are worried the extra time needed will make you miss your shift at work."]
            },
            {
              "name": "1",
              "text": ["By mustering up the courage to ask for an extension, you were able to take some stress off. At the same time, your teacher became more aware of your situation and paid more attention to your needs as a student. Subsequently, you were able to go to work for the day and made some extra cash for the family."]
            },
            {
              "name": "2",
              "text": ["Staying up all night to complete your work was alot of stress for you, and you did not get enough sleep for the next day. You were also unable to report to work and lost out on the day's earnings. "]
            }
          ],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "name": "teacher",
              "speeches": [
                {
                  "character": "Teacher",
                  "text": "Curtis, the assignment you handed in last week was poorly done. I'd like you bring this home, redo the assignment and hand it to me tomorrow."
                },
                {
                  "character": "Curtis",
                  "text": "Okay, thank you sir."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "inner",
              "speeches": [
                {
                  "character": "Curtis",
                  "text": "I can't believe I have to redo my assignment... I'm pretty sure I did it correctly, or maybe I was too tired when I first did it?"
                },
                {
                  "character": "Curtis",
                  "text": "Eitherway, I definitely do not have enough time to complete it by tomrrow, I need to go to work later, and I still need to go home and tend to my siblings. If I were to finish my assignment, I won't have much time to sleep and rest tonight! "
                },
                {
                  "character": "Curtis",
                  "text": "Should I just try and complete the assignment? Or maybe I should speak to my teacher...."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "after",
              "speeches": [
                {
                  "character": "Curtis",
                  "text": "Ummm, excuse me sir, is it okay if I request for an extension for this assignment? I have to go to work later to help support my family, and I need to prepare dinner for my family as well. I don't think I have the time to complete the assignment by tomorrow."
                },
                {
                  "character": "Teacher",
                  "text": "Oh! I was not totally aware of your situation. I apologise. Sure, you don't need to submit it tomorrow, how about by the end of next week?"
                },
                {
                  "character": "Curtis",
                  "text": "Yes, that would work! Thank you so much!"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
